{"tid":1590482,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"又有人死啦","createTime":"2019-09-23T17:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T17:36:55.000Z","uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd279e142892ddae6cb55d93c15e55882ead223a","tid":1590482,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:33:59.000Z","msg":"[西環突發] 有冇人知咩事？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590393\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590393</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n係對面行過，心諗唔係又被自殺呀？結果係有人自殺冇可疑，你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190924/60077646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190924%2F60077646&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=4e994635\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190924%2F60077646&h=7e80d52c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190924/60077646</a><br />\n<br />\n西環皇后大道西419號，昨晚11時許，一名中年男子，從大廈高處墮下，身軀壓毀毗鄰大廈地下停車場閘口的欄杆，墮地昏迷不醒，救護員趕至現場，惟證實男子已當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警員封鎖展開調查，死者並非大廈住客，初步相信死者尾隨住客進入大廈，再走上12樓天台，攀出圍欄墮樓死亡，案件並無可疑。"},{"pid":"0857903303f339e002688a8542809baa375895d7","tid":1590482,"uid":99883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:34:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死者並非大廈住客<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"1292978a088ab1ce669d9ef2154a9582092a4aea","tid":1590482,"uid":4760